description:
I'm not a very focused person. Today we jump around the place looking a various awesome inventions. One of the projects I work on is trying to improve a skeleton mob separator invented by YouTuber, BDtetra. You can check out his v1.1 here:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=35bu5UZIcPE

We also check out a cool boat powered warp speed invention sent to me nanometer789.
